{"tid":528754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女行車天橋躍下　墮百呎身亡","createTime":"2018-01-14T07:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T19:16:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"df2ad940345bb7598d94af2a819dc797871ad862","tid":528754,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"警方稱，死者姓林17歲<br />\n<br />\n上午11時半，一名女子被途人發現，倒卧在青衣西路公園旁邊一條小徑，昏迷不醒，救護員到場經檢驗證實她已告不治。警方調查後，懷疑她由長亨邨對開青衣西路的行車天橋上，攀越欄河一躍而下，飛跌落約30米(約100呎)下的小徑。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查得悉死者姓林17歲，現場沒有撿獲遺書，尋死原因有待進一步了解，事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"ca783451aaa4d31647e88785fbc422bb860bd4ef","tid":528754,"uid":55488,"like":3,"dislike":80,"score":-77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed6ec2fbaa2be80822db6a32d5b68b2ce326a4c0","tid":528754,"uid":25221,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94cd4e7aca843d2d777cd1798398101617a5c129","tid":528754,"uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"LM等睇變態佬"},{"pid":"a48516902f34606d939f9076a09ea52b654eff6f","tid":528754,"uid":69886,"like":8,"dislike":101,"score":-93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"可能件臭閪比人中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a37bfc348d0ceb5b8ef585a7f0e4300231afc8","tid":528754,"uid":147540,"like":29,"dislike":112,"score":-83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e988c492db7f4e4b193ed9cef98463497fa39d7","tid":528754,"uid":38820,"like":3,"dislike":49,"score":-46,"quote":{"pid":"33a37bfc348d0ceb5b8ef585a7f0e4300231afc8","tid":528754,"uid":147540,"like":29,"dislike":112,"score":-83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:02